dct_alternative_sm: Fort Head to Kinchow including Kwangtung Bay
dct_description_sm: From a Japanese survey in 1907 with additions from a British survey in 1860 ; published Feb., 1916, at the Hydrographic Office, under the authority of the Secretary of the Navy.
Depths shown by soundings; relief by form lines and spot heights.
Inset chart: "Pulantien Kiang (Continuation on same scale from below)."
Shows shoals, reefs, islands, currents, cultivated land, drainage, towns, buildings, roads, railways.
